{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a, a nice house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like in Holland, they have a shop, and then you have the kitchen and the-- at the back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you go upstairs, and there were bedrooms and another attic, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it wasn't-- the time that we lived there, when this all happened, I remember my father sort of saying to my mother, we have to move from here.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have to go from here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The reason being also because my father had given two of those soldiers which escaped from that army barracks-- they were normal Dutch soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had run into our shop, and they had said, give us civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Give us civilian clothes immediately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father didn't have-- I mean, he only had his own suits.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember that performance, because I remember my father taking clothes out of the cupboards and saying, take this, take this, and, and wear this, and-- you know, quick, because it was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think those two men were actually caught running.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- it's a little bit sketchy for me, because I remember, like, my father saying, it's too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's much too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, my dad lended-- the, the, the Nazi party came in on him and said, you've given these people help, and we're going to take you to jail.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father went to jail for a little while there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother knew someone that was involved with the-- it was like a socialist party, who she used to have dealings with in auctions in times of when they were buying furniture.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went up to this man and said, look, you've got to do something for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
